Package: xwiimote
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: download and run games from itch.io
  The goal of this project is to give you a desktop application 
  that you can download and run games from itch.io with. Additionally 
  you should be able to update games and get notified when games are 
  updated. The goal is not to replace the itch.io website.
  .
  This software is hosted at:
  https://github.com/itchio/itch
  
